# ai/AGENTS.manifest — concat order for ~/.codex/AGENTS.md build
# One file per line, paths relative to ~/.config/ai/. Comments via `#`.
# feedback_ai_config_structure.md MUST be the first memory entry (carries token substitution).

# Top-level metas
PERSONAL.md
guardrails.md

# Rules (alphabetical by topic)
rules/code-review.md
rules/diagnostics.md
rules/rationalization.md
rules/testing.md

# Memory (config-structure rules first — enables all later tokens)
memory/feedback_ai_config_structure.md
memory/feedback_no_guessing.md
memory/feedback_prompt_format.md
memory/feedback_reverse_grep.md
memory/feedback_code_review_per_commit.md
memory/feedback_raw_urls.md
memory/feedback_memory_english.md
memory/feedback_global_memory_path.md

# Private memory (gitignored — only readable on the local machine)
memory/private/reference_naver_tools.md
memory/private/feedback_pre_commit_sensitive_scan.md
